## 9. Notes for Build Planning
- Keep button/modal behavior aligned with existing Opportunity premium-edit UX patterns
- Reuse existing lock-state checks where possible
- Add explicit guard in cancellation/cancel-and-reissue cloning paths to enforce MLIS non-returnable and correction rules
